Prompt for Image Generation:
Create an image depicting a majestic and awe-inspiring mountain peak reaching up towards the heavens, shrouded in mist and bathed in a divine light. At the summit of the mountain, show a powerful yet gentle presence emanating a sense of transcendence and divine glory, symbolizing the concept of God as transcendent in Christian theology. Surround the scene with a peaceful and reverent atmosphere, invoking a sense of wonder and reverence for the divine.
